milestones.description: Glenn Turner and Bruce Edgar's 152-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 113 between John Wright and Bruce Edgar
Glenn Turner and Bruce Edgar's 152-run partnership is NZ's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 149 between John Parker and Glenn Turner
Glenn Turner has scored 10 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking John Wright's record
